              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Invoque un </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Gooba</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/26fc236bd113d2bcb3ea4b2e946fefe3_1184611131930455921.png",
                "id": "talent19380",
                "key": "Attaque Gooba",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Attaque Gooba"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et crée une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyrotation</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pyrotation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorsque votre personnage a utilisé une capacité : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/f10ee07430ab7e5e55a9263695844987_3046512771962310832.png",
                "id": "talent18273",
                "key": "Pyrotation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyrotation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Invocation</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase final : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5093169622804401206.png",
                "id": "talent63626",
                "key": "Gooba",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/e2813d89dc49ef548d3b82cf9b277a04_8342403798750410619.png",
                "title": "Gooba"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Pyro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fonte </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Évaporation </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Surcharge </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2 et bascule de force la cible pour le personnage suivant</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Brûlure </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +1 et crée une </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">flamme brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> qui inflige des DGT Pyro à la fin de la manche (Utilisable 1 fois, 2 cumuls maximum)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2968151385091020627.png",
                "id": "talent87083",
                "key": "DGT Pyro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Pyro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT physiques</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT physiques n'appliquent aucun élément et ne peuvent pas non plus déclencher de réactions élémentaires.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35653081/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8465162889923778840.png",
